With every head bowed, every eye closed in this room, if you're here today and you know for a fact, you have a broken relationship with God.

34:04.295 --> 34:07.218
Or for some of you, you've never had a real relationship with God.

34:08.239 --> 34:09.641
Can I lead you in that moment?

34:10.622 --> 34:12.584
In fact, at every location, be very still.

34:13.305 --> 34:17.330
And as you're here today, you say, Chris, God feels like a million miles away.

34:18.471 --> 34:24.498
The Bible says that Jesus came to pay for sin to make you and God close again.

34:25.282 --> 34:28.026
And that closeness, listen to me, can happen in one prayer.

34:29.348 --> 34:32.773
I'm not talking about joining this church, although that'd be a good thing for you to do.

34:33.094 --> 34:37.200
I'm talking about joining Jesus and making him the Lord of your life.

34:38.582 --> 34:43.469
And if you're prepared to do that, the Bible says you can do it by the confession of your mouth to make him the Lord of your life.

34:43.990 --> 34:45.833
And I'll lead you in that prayer right now.

34:46.734 --> 34:52.162
If that's you, say these words, whisper them right there in your seat and say, Jesus, forgive me.

34:53.304 --> 34:54.866
I lived my life

34:55.266 --> 34:56.087
away from you.

34:57.068 --> 34:57.929
I lived it my way.

34:59.431 --> 35:03.516
And today I'm inviting you to be the Lord of my life.

35:04.878 --> 35:08.622
I'm prepared to surrender my life to you everything.

35:09.944 --> 35:10.765
So take my life.

35:11.546 --> 35:12.207
Forgive me.

35:13.308 --> 35:13.829
Save me.

35:14.710 --> 35:17.573
And Holy Spirit, come live inside of me.

35:18.294 --> 35:21.618
In fact, be alive only inside of me.

35:23.170 --> 35:29.442
Because I truly believe that Jesus is the Son of God who was raised from the dead.

35:30.304 --> 35:38.400
And today I put my faith and my trust and my love and my devotion in Him.

35:39.122 --> 35:40.484
In Jesus' name I pray.

35:41.006 --> 35:41.266
Amen.

